Flora of Virginia
*Galax urceolata* (Poiret) Brum.
near Sherando, Augusta Co.
Colony of 100's along edges of upper
Orebank Creek by Turkey Pen Ridge Trail.
With *Osmunda cinnamomea*, *Lycopodium obscurum*,
*Gaultheria* & *Rubus hispidus* in oak-pine-gum-
maple woods ca. 3 mi. SW of Sherando.
(Sherando Quad.)
